profileNotes: The Void Pure is a specialized build focused on using the Void Knight equipment set to maximize combat effectiveness. The build achieves a balance between Attack, Strength, and Defence at level 42, which allows equipping the Void Knight set. With 99 Ranged and Magic, this build delivers high DPS using ranged and magic attacks. The 55 Prayer level grants access to the Preserve prayer and higher-tier offensive prayers, while 99 Hitpoints maximizes survivability. This build is suitable for PvP scenarios and PvM content where Void equipment is advantageous.
